This directory/diskette contains postscript files for possible 
distribution for a short course on Quantile Regression prepared
for the 5th School on Regression Models, to be held February 26-28
in Campos dos Jordao, SP, Brazil.  They consist of the following

readme		This file
title2.ps	Title page for the monograph file
book.ps		Chapters 1-3 of a monograph-in-progress
s3.ps		Manuscript of a paper on ranktests
haretort.ps	Manuscript of a paper on Computation


I will probably not have time to say much about either of the two papers,
and therefore it is not essential that they be distributed for the conference,
but I would like to present the computation paper in the seminars
which have been arranged in conjunction with the conference,
so I thought that I would include it.  The survey paper includes some
related material, particularly on time-series which I thought might be
a useful supplement to the monograph material.


Roger Koenker
